{"tid":1563883,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"｛915國際民主日｝國旗飄揚 遍地開花","createTime":"2019-09-12T14:31:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-13T00:03:40.000Z","uid":153186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8149b2eb318be6369baa0a97a276080f47f87dc8","tid":1563883,"uid":153186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T14:31:01.000Z","msg":"大佬們 美、德、英三個國家打晒開口牌 共匪次次驚到叫救命 你地唔係咩都唔做下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當致謝又好 請願又好 引外媒報道又好 國旗海一定最吸睛 唔該你地一人一支旗先好出黎行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實唔洗買 用A3紙print出黎貼係心口/背囊就可以（真係唔得就A4print多幾張出黎照殺啦）咁簡單一齊做啦！<br />\n<br />\n915國旗飄揚 遍地開花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[img]<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zoXsgS4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzoXsgS4.png&h=1d2cfd4e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i0Zm5Mr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi0Zm5Mr.png&h=0faf7313&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"https://na.cx/i/gkuKi3A.png[/img]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgkuKi3A.png%5B%2Fimg%5D&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=19e6c3fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/gkuKi3A.png[/img]</a><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zgLmmgW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzgLmmgW.png&h=8e2ab122&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/p5G43vg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fp5G43vg.png&h=de011d98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zqnjSoC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb